        <Parent_String>Levantine Paleolithic periods [300019576], Levantine periods [300107629], Levantine (culture or style) [300019811], Near Eastern (Early Western World) [300019571], Early Western World [300019255], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
